videos.headline: Arizona's McDonald drains a 3 off the inbound pass
videos.description: Aari McDonald receives the inbound pass and pulls up to drain a 3-pointer in the defender's face to give Arizona a 46-40 lead over Texas A&M.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Arizona's McDonald drains a 3 off the inbound pass) 2021/03/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: McDonald fired up after getting friendly bounce from downtown
videos.description: Aari McDonald poses as she gets a friendly bounce on a 3-point shot, then lets out a fiery yell as Texas A&M calls a timeout.
